yle=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18)); color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85));&quot;&gt;на доработку бизнес-процессов приема и обработки заказов через интернет-магазин &quot;Переделкино&quot;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- Выгрузка с данными, которые клиенты указывали при оформлении заказа.&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Карточка товаров.&lt;br&gt;- Данные поставщиков.&lt;br&gt;- Список промокодов для проведения скидок.                                                                                                                  &lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- Тарифы на доставку и дополнительные услуги.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18)); color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); box-sizing: inherit;&quot;&gt;2.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18)); color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85));&quot;&gt; Классы CRM и их краткое описание&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(236, 236, 236);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18)); color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Покупатель: содержит информацию, которая хранится в Профиле покупателя, а именно&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;id&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;покупателя&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(236, 236, 236);&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237)); white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: light-dark(rgb(236, 236, 236), rgb(34, 34, 34));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;ФИО,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237)); white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: light-dark(rgb(236, 236, 236), rgb(34, 34, 34));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Дата рождения,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237)); white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: light-dark(rgb(236, 236, 236), rgb(34, 34, 34));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(236, 236, 236), rgb(34, 34, 34)); color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;Телефон,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Адрес,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;Количество заказов, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;Список заказов&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;. Этот класс связан с классом Заказ.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot; face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Заказ: &lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;это информация о принятом в систему заказе товаров,произведенным покупателем. Содержит&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&amp;nbsp;id заказа и&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;покупателя,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;id магазина (из которого будет производится доставка или самовывоз),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;id промокода (в случае его применения к заказу),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;id оплаты,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;id заявки на доставку (в случае ее наличия),&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;id заявки на самовывоз (в случае ее наличия),&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Д&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;ату создания,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Сумму,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Статус заказа (В обработке/Передан в доставку/Передан в магазин/Выдан/Отменен),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;Список товаров&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Приоритетный вид связи по заказу (Звонок/ Сообщение). Связан со всеми классами, кроме Поставщик&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;и Сотрудник&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- Товар:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18)); white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;описывает товар, добавленный покупателем в заказ. Хранит&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;id товара,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;id поставщика, i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;d магазина (в котором хранится товар),&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Товарный код,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Товарное наименование&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Категорию товара,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Количество товара на складе,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Штрихкод,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Вес товара,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Код поставщика,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Срок хранения,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Высоту, ширину, длину упаковки,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Цену и&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Себестоимость&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;товара. Связан с классом Заказ и Поставщик .&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;- Поставщик:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;это информация о внесенном в базу Поставщике товаров. Содержит &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;id поставщика,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;Наименование,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;ИНН, КПП, ОГРН,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Телефон,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Город,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;Адрес,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;E-mail,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Дату заключения договора с поставщиком,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;Список поставляемых товаров&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;. Класс связан только с классом Товар.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;- Заявка на доставку:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;это информация о принятой заявке на доставку товаров. Содержит&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;id заявки на доставку,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(236, 236, 236); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;id заказа,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;id магазина (из которого будет производится доставка),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;id сотрудника, подтвердившего заказ,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;id сотрудника, собравшего заказ,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot; style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;Дату доставки,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Время доставки (временной интервал),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;Телефон получателя доставки,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Адрес доставки&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Зона доставки (определяется исходя из адреса доставки и может быть 1/2/3/4/5),&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;Этаж,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Подъем на этаж (Да/Нет),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Стоимость доставки (рассчитывается исходя из зоны доставки),&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;Список товаров&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; white-space-collapse: collapse; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18)); white-space-collapse: collapse; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Связан с классом Заказ, Магазин, Сотрудник.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;- Заявка на самовывоз:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;это информация о принятой заявке на выдачу заказа в магазине (самовывоз). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Хранит&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;id заявки на самовывоз,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;id заказа,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;id магазина,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;id сотрудника, подтвердившего заказ,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;id сотрудника, собравшего заказ,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Дата оформления заказа,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Статус оплаты,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Список товаров&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot; style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Связан с классом Заказ,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Магазин, Сотрудник&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot; style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- Оплата:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;это информация об оплате заказа. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot; style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Содержит&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;id оплаты,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;id заказа,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Дата,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Сумма,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Способ оплаты (Онлайн банковской картой/ Онлайн через СБП/ В магазине),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Статус (Нет оплаты/Оплата подтверждена/Оплата возвращена).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Связан с классом Заказ.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- Промокод: это информация о промокодах, доступных покупателям для ввода, содержит&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&amp;nbsp;id промокода,&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Название промокода,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Размер скидки,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Условия применения,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Дату начала акции,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;Дату окончания акции,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Количество применений на одного пользователя.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot;&gt;Связан с классом Заказ.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;- Магазин:&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;это информация о  магазинах сети. Хранит сведения:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;id магазина,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Название филиала,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Адрес,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Список товаров на складе,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Список заявок на доставку,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Список заявок на самовывоз.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Связан с классом Заказ, Сотрудник, Заявка на доставку, Заявка на самовывоз.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- Сотрудник:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;это информация о сотрудниках магазинов. Содержит &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;id сотрудника,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;id магазина,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;ФИО,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Должность,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Статус (Работает/Уволен). Связан с классом Магазин, Заявка на доставку, Заявка на самовывоз.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit;&quot;&gt;3. С&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;b&gt;вязи между классами CRM&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;Классы Заявка на доставку, Заявка на самовывоз, Оплата &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span&gt;связаны с классом &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Заказ &lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot; style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;связью типа &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); box-sizing: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;Композиция. В случае отмены заказа &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85));&quot;&gt;Заявка на доставку, Заявка на самовывоз, Оплата тоже перестают существовать (заявки отменяются, оплата возвращается клиенту).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Класс Сотрудник связан с классом Магазин связью Агрегация. В случае закрытия магазина, сотрудники могут быть переведены в другое подразделение и продолжить работу.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.85)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;Остальные связи между классами - Ассоциация.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="1070" width="760" x="20" y="-1070" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
